ים מאיר בכפר סבא, שם נקבע מותו לאחר זמן קצר, וחשודים טרם נעצרו.","case_narrative_en":"Abd Al-Rahim Abd Al-Latif Salameh, 50, was killed on March 22, 2022, in a shooting incident in Qalansawe. He sustained serious injuries after being shot approximately 30 times while inside his vehicle near his home. Salameh was transported to Meir Hospital in Kfar Saba, where he was pronounced dead, and no suspects have been apprehended.","review_status":"auto","pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2022-01-01_2022-12-31","enrichment_passes":0,"_pipeline_run_id":"canonical_2022-01-01_2022-12-31","run_id":"canonical","case_index":779}